00:27:11,663 --> 00:27:13,164
Oh...
Remember?

639
00:27:13,164 --> 00:27:17,168
Mm. Do you remember
Nono's wedding cake?

640
00:27:17,168 --> 00:27:18,670
Yeah, I remember.

641
00:27:20,171 --> 00:27:22,674
You know how it kind of...
it kind of...

